Package com.xd.cps2002.player

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Player
    The Player class defines a player in the game, and is responsible for calculating the new Position after a move.
    PlayerTest
    Tester class for the Player class.
    Position
    Simple convenience class to maintain (x,y)--coordinates (representative of indices).
    PositionTest
    Tester class for the Position class.
    Team
    The Team class defines the notion of a team in the game, and is responsible for maintaining the collective history of all players forming part of the team.
    TeamTest
    Tester class for the Team class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PlayerStatus
    The PlayerStatus enum defines the different states/outcome that can happen as a result of the player moving to a specific tile.
